{"tid":1231524,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"表示政府現階段撤回修例，就會令人覺得修例是無立足之地","createTime":"2019-06-16T13:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T13:22:58.000Z","uid":58750,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9d276954c5da4fea1fb98e0a0d0f929ed2414f1d","tid":1231524,"uid":58750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:02:16.000Z","msg":"政府：已停止立法會大會對修訂《逃犯條例》 工作<br />\n2019-06-16 HKT 20:37<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，考慮社會有強烈不同意見，已停止立法會大會對修訂《逃犯條例》的工作。發言人說，希望藉此可讓社會盡快回復平靜和避免任何人受到傷害，重申並無重啟程序的時間表。<br />\n<br />\n政府晚上透過新聞稿回應遊行，說行政長官承認由於政府工作上不足，令香港出現很大矛盾和紛爭，令很多市民感到失望和痛心，行政長官為此向市民致歉，並承諾會以最有誠意、最謙卑的態度接受批評，加以改進，為市民服務。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>昨日行政長官林鄭月娥見記者時，表示政府決定暫緩修例工作，又說如果現階段撤回修例，就會令人覺得修例是無立足之地。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463241-20190616.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463241-20190616.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypyQsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=e09a29a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463241-20190616.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c90bc4c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463241-20190616.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a05f72a0600e4206596b2fa0b4fef64cf1f01b6f","tid":1231524,"uid":58750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:02:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a5ee2cb0ece506970b73250d400da3bfe937b719","tid":1231524,"uid":58750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:03:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6abc61bfe55a757e2b3714a2d35fb3fed59f1953","tid":1231524,"uid":58750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:04:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4514aa7b8f487dc65757c2ccf94dea5203aeb06f","tid":1231524,"uid":48251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:21:47.000Z","msg":"屌你老母呀"},{"pid":"3728bf019db5a71b97217bbb736dd8745ffc263b","tid":1231524,"uid":48251,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:22:58.000Z","msg":"呢個香港政府除左面子已經咩都無？"}]}